Universe Mongae

Korean: 우주멍게

Hometown:

Seoul

Country:

South Korea

Introduction

Universe Mongae (우주멍게) is a South Korean electronic pop musician. She debuted with the digital single 'MORPH+NE' on June 14th, 2016. MORPH+NE was exclusively released on Bandcamp, Soundcloud, and on South Korean streaming services. Before she made her debut, she released five songs on Soundcloud, one of which was a cover of Wasted by Dreezy.
